{"tid":2247381,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方拘捕10名男子 涉非法入境及協助教唆非法入境","createTime":"2020-10-17T19:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T03:46:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef7a201aa8866c6c449d8c5065d541628aacbd6b","tid":2247381,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T19:09:33.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕10名男子，分別涉嫌非法入境，及協助及教唆他人非法入境。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚近9時接報，指大嶼山懷疑有非法入境者，警員在嶼南道近水口村，及東涌道近伯公坳對開，截停兩輛的士。的士上8名內地男子涉嫌非法入境被捕，其餘兩名的士司機則涉嫌協助及教唆他人非法入境被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555329-20201018.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555329-20201018.htm&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPSIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=d386fe10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555329-20201018.htm&h=7840484a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555329-20201018.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4f77424e816b3c8e3860bb90f460ec2397e19dd2","tid":2247381,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de258c052ac4c26c73e078d9569cbccffd8a0086","tid":2247381,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T19:12:46.000Z","msg":"以為又捉非法出境"},{"pid":"9a7f9708a29ed12f23208f2145d7a68f8237f69d","tid":2247381,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f77424e816b3c8e3860bb90f460ec2397e19dd2","tid":2247381,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gi